# habitseeding — Cursor AI Design System Rules
# "Morning Garden" Calm Palette
# Updated from design critique · 2026-03-13
#
# These rules govern every Flutter file you generate or modify in this project.
# Follow them strictly. When in doubt, reference AppColors, AppTypography, and
# AppColors.lightScheme / darkScheme as the source of truth.
#
# Core design principle: every color, spacing, and type choice should feel like
# 6 AM in a quiet garden — warm, grounded, alive, and never loud.
# habitseeding is about planting small habits and watching them grow.
# The UI must feel calm enough to open every morning without anxiety.

---

## 1. PROJECT IDENTITY

- App name: Digital Vision Board
- Package name: habitseeding (flutter package: digital_vision_board)
- Design metaphor: "Morning Garden" — warm soil, sage growth, honey seeds, morning mist
- Platform: Flutter (iOS · Android · Web · Desktop)
- State: Provider + SharedPreferences (no Riverpod/Bloc unless already present)
- Vibe check: if a widget feels loud, bright, or clinical, it is wrong for this app.

---

## 2. COLOR — USE THESE, NOTHING ELSE

### 2a. The "Morning Garden" Palette

Every color has a name and a purpose rooted in the seeding metaphor.
The palette is warm, muted, and earthy — never neon, never cold.

```
LIGHT MODE
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NAME              TOKEN / USAGE                       HEX        CONTRAST*
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Warm Cream Mist   AppColors.mistBackground             #F6F4EF    — (bg)
Sage Morning Haze AppColors.skyTopTint                 #EAF2EA    — (bg top)
Sage Leaf         AppColors.sproutGreen (primary CTA)  #4A7A5A    4.9:1 ✅
Warm Soil         AppColors.forestDeep (nav, headings) #3B2D20   13.7:1 ✅
Honey Amber       AppColors.seedGold (icon/badge fill) #C48B3C    2.9:1 ⚠️
Honey Text        AppColors.honeyText (amber text use) #7A5520    6.7:1 ✅
Pale Sage         AppColors.sageContainer (chips/rows) #DCF0E4    — (container)
Pale Honey        AppColors.seedChampagne (badge bg)   #FDF3E3    — (container)
Lavender Dew      AppColors.lavenderDew (mood/journal) #7B74A8    4.6:1 ✅
Pale Lavender     AppColors.lavenderContainer          #EEEDF8    — (container)
Card Surface      AppColors.cloudWhite                 #FFFFFF    — (card)

DARK MODE
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Night Soil        colorScheme.surface (dark)           #0F1510    — (bg)
Warm Grove Card   AppColors.cloudDark                  #1F2B22    — (card)
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
* Contrast vs white background
```

### 2b. Semantic Usage Map

| What you're building               | Color to use                              |
|------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| Page background                    | `AppColors.skyDecoration(isDark: isDark)` |
| Screen scaffold background color   | `colorScheme.surface`                     |
| Primary button / FAB               | `colorScheme.primary` (#4A7A5A sage)      |
| Primary button text                | `colorScheme.onPrimary` (white)           |
| Bottom nav background              | `AppColors.forestDeep` (#3B2D20 soil)     |
| Active nav icon + label            | `AppColors.sproutGreen` (#4A7A5A)         |
| Inactive nav icon + label          | `AppColors.sproutGreen.withValues(alpha: 0.45)` |
| Section header / screen title text | `colorScheme.onSurface` (warm soil)       |
| Secondary / hint text              | `colorScheme.onSurfaceVariant` (#5C4E40)  |
| Content card                       | `AppColors.cloudDecoration(isDark: isDark)` |
| Glass card (over photo/image bg)   | `GlassCard` widget                        |
| Coin / badge icon fill             | `AppColors.seedGold` (#C48B3C)            |
| Coin / badge as text               | `AppColors.honeyText` (#7A5520) ← ALWAYS |
| Habit streak / progress ring       | `colorScheme.primary`                     |
| Completion checkmark               | `colorScheme.primary`                     |
| Mood / journal / affirmation       | `AppColors.lavenderDew` (#7B74A8)         |
| Chips, selected rows, tags         | `AppColors.sageContainer` (#DCF0E4) bg    |
| Error states                       | `colorScheme.error`                       |
| Dividers / outlines                | `colorScheme.outlineVariant`              |

### 2c. Code Patterns — Correct vs Wrong

```dart
// ✅ CORRECT — via ColorScheme (preferred for most UI)
final cs = Theme.of(context).colorScheme;
final isDark = cs.brightness == Brightness.dark;
Container(color: cs.surface)
Text('Today', style: TextStyle(color: cs.onSurface))

// ✅ CORRECT — via AppColors for the 3 always-fixed tokens
Container(decoration: AppColors.skyDecoration(isDark: isDark))  // page bg
Container(decoration: AppColors.cloudDecoration(isDark: isDark)) // card
// bottom nav bg only:
color: AppColors.forestDeep

// ✅ CORRECT — amber text (honey meaning)
Text('🌱 +50 seeds', style: TextStyle(color: AppColors.honeyText))

// ✅ CORRECT — sage text (completion/growth meaning)
Text('Done', style: TextStyle(color: cs.onPrimaryContainer))

// ❌ WRONG — hardcoded hex
Container(color: const Color(0xFF4A7A5A))

// ❌ WRONG — old neon green
Container(color: const Color(0xFF4CAF50))

// ❌ WRONG — honey amber as text (fails contrast)
Text('50 seeds', style: TextStyle(color: AppColors.seedGold))

// ❌ WRONG — bare white Scaffold (breaks warm background system)
Scaffold(backgroundColor: Colors.white)
```

### 2d. WCAG AA Compliance Summary

| Pairing                                       | Ratio  | Status |
|-----------------------------------------------|--------|--------|
| `forestDeep` (#3B2D20) on white               | 13.7:1 | ✅ AAA |
| `forestDeep` on `mistBackground`              | 12.8:1 | ✅ AAA |
| `sproutGreen` (#4A7A5A) on white              | 4.9:1  | ✅ AA  |
| `sproutGreen` on `mistBackground`             | 4.6:1  | ✅ AA  |
| `lavenderDew` (#7B74A8) on white              | 4.6:1  | ✅ AA  |
| `honeyText` (#7A5520) on white                | 6.7:1  | ✅ AA  |
| `onSurfaceVariant` (#5C4E40) on `mistBg`      | 5.8:1  | ✅ AA  |
| `seedGold` (#C48B3C) on white — ICON ONLY     | 2.9:1  | ❌ text fails — use honeyText for text |
| white on `sproutGreen` — button labels        | 4.9:1  | ✅ AA  |

### 2e. Legacy Colors — DEPRECATED

Do NOT use in new code. These existed in the old "Digital Greenhouse" palette.

```
AppColors.dark, .darkest, .medium, .light, .lightest
AppColors.mintGreen, .sageGreen, .mossGreen, .forestGreen, .gold
AppColors.soilLight, .soilDark, .soilMedium
AppColors.seedLight, .seedDark, .seedDeep
AppColors.waterLight, .waterDark
AppColors.skyGradientTopLight/Dark, .skyGradientBottomLight/Dark → use skyDecoration()
AppColors.cloudLight → use cloudWhite
```

### 2f. Feature-Specific Color Accents

These are pre-assigned. Do NOT reassign features to different accent colors.

| Feature domain       | Accent color                   | Use for              |
|----------------------|--------------------------------|----------------------|
| Mood tracking        | `AppColors.lavenderDew`        | Icons, chips, header |
| Journal / writing    | `AppColors.lavenderDew`        | Cover tint, icon     |
| Affirmations         | `AppColors.lavenderDew`        | Card accent          |
| Habits / streaks     | `colorScheme.primary` (sage)   | Rings, checkmarks    |
| Vision boards        | `colorScheme.primary` (sage)   | Active state         |
| Coins / rewards      | `AppColors.seedGold` (fill only) | Icon, badge fill   |
| Completion / done    | `AppColors.completedOrange`    | Completed state      |
| Habit categories     | `AppColors.categoryBgColor()`  | Category circles     |

